  <description>
    <p>ACBR is a free and open source comic book reader and converter that supports CBZ, CBR, CB7, PDF, EPUB, JPG, PNG, WebP and AVIF files.</p>
    <p>Besides the tools to convert and create comic books and images, it also includes an RSS reader, integrated audio player, internet radio... and some other extras.</p>   
